snippet.title: Jason Momoa Reveals He Wants Amber Heard Fired From Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
►Jason Momoa Reveals He Wants Amber Heard Fired From Aquaman 2
Warner Bros. has announced that Amber Heard has been sacked from the sequel to Jason Momoa's Aquaman, according to Popcorned Planet. Her dismissal is due to her failure to comply with several health-related restrictions. Emilia Clarke has not been selected to replace Heard, according to the video.
